{"prompt": "Build an intuitive platform for an online recipe sharing community. The design should prominently display a vibrant cherry red.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Recipe Share</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #E63946; /* Cherry Red */\n            --secondary-color: #F1FAEE; /* Off-white */\n            --text-color: #1D3557; /* Dark Blue */\n            --accent-color: #A8DADC; /* Light Blue */\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 1rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5rem;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 0.8rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 1rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            padding: 0 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .recipe-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .recipe-card {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n\n        .recipe-card:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        .recipe-card img {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        .recipe-content {\n            padding: 1rem;\n            flex-grow: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            justify-content: space-between;\n        }\n\n        .recipe-content h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            font-size: 1.4rem;\n        }\n\n        .recipe-content p {\n            font-size: 0.95rem;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        .recipe-actions a {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 0.6rem 1rem;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-top: 0.5rem;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .recipe-actions a:hover {\n            background-color: #c2303a;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 1.5rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .search-bar {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n        }\n\n        .search-bar input[type=\"text\"] {\n            padding: 0.8rem;\n            width: 60%;\n            border: 1px solid var(--accent-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .search-bar button {\n            padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--secondary-color);\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1rem;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .search-bar button:hover {\n            background-color: #c2303a;\n        }\n\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Recipe Share</h1>\n        <p>Discover and share your favorite recipes</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#\">Home</a>\n        <a href=\"#\">Browse Recipes</a>\n        <a href=\"#\">Submit Recipe</a>\n        <a href=\"#\">About</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"search-bar\">\n            <input type=\"text\" id=\"searchQuery\" placeholder=\"Search for recipes...\">\n            <button onclick=\"searchRecipes()\">Search</button>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"recipe-grid\" id=\"recipeList\">\n            <div class=\"recipe-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/E63946/FFFFFF?text=Spicy+Chicken+Curry\" alt=\"Spicy Chicken Curry\">\n                <div class=\"recipe-content\">\n                    <h3>Spicy Chicken Curry</h3>\n                    <p>A flavorful and aromatic chicken curry with a kick. Perfect for a weeknight dinner.</p>\n                    <div class=\"recipe-actions\">\n                        <a href=\"#\">View Recipe</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"recipe-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/A8DADC/1D3557?text=Vegan+Lentil+Soup\" alt=\"Vegan Lentil Soup\">\n                <div class=\"recipe-content\">\n                    <h3>Vegan Lentil Soup</h3>\n                    <p>Hearty and healthy, this vegan lentil soup is packed with vegetables and protein.</p>\n                    <div class=\"recipe-actions\">\n                        <a href=\"#\">View Recipe</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"recipe-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/F1FAEE/E63946?text=Chocolate+Lava+Cake\" alt=\"Chocolate Lava Cake\">\n                <div class=\"recipe-content\">\n                    <h3>Chocolate Lava Cake</h3>\n                    <p>Indulge in this decadent chocolate lava cake with a gooey, molten center.</p>\n                    <div class=\"recipe-actions\">\n                        <a href=\"#\">View Recipe</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"recipe-card\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/1D3557/FFFFFF?text=Quick+Pasta+Primavera\" alt=\"Quick Pasta Primavera\">\n                <div class=\"recipe-content\">\n                    <h3>Quick Pasta Primavera</h3>\n                    <p>A vibrant and easy pasta dish loaded with fresh seasonal vegetables.</p>\n                    <div class=\"recipe-actions\">\n                        <a href=\"#\">View Recipe</a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Recipe Share. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        function searchRecipes() {\n            const searchQuery = document.getElementById('searchQuery').value.toLowerCase();\n            const recipeCards = document.querySelectorAll('.recipe-card');\n\n            recipeCards.forEach(card => {\n                const recipeTitle = card.querySelector('h3').textContent.toLowerCase();\n                const recipeDescription = card.querySelector('p').textContent.toLowerCase();\n\n                if (recipeTitle.includes(searchQuery) || recipeDescription.includes(searchQuery)) {\n                    card.style.display = 'flex';\n                } else {\n                    card.style.display = 'none';\n                }\n            });\n        }\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}